        "title": "Summary by Priority",
        "content": "| Priority | Area | Risk | Key Gap |\n|----------|------|------|---------|\n| 1 | `HistoryOfThought` crypto | Critical | AES-GCM round-trip, vault lock soft-drop |\n| 2 | `ExecutiveSpine` state | Critical | Focus sessions, health thresholds, credits |\n| 3 | `LiteralMode` patterns | High | 20+ regex replacements, edge cases |\n| 4 | `EventBus` pipeline | High | Silent-drop on vault lock unverified |\n| 5 | `BriefService` / `MicroStepService` | High | Regex extraction, Ollama fallback |\n| 6 | `IndexedDBService` / `SovereignReconciler` | Medium | Storage round-trips, deduplication |\n\nThe encryption layer and focus session state are the highest-risk untested paths given they underpin the academic authenticity and productivity claims of the system.",
